{"tid":1039924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男遭綁架餵吃硬硬藥　逼跟男啪啪啪23小時","createTime":"2019-02-27T17:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T09:37:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4b422a45f8efc146a16320a9d15efd62424f66be","tid":1039924,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"南非一名50歲男子被綁架後，綁匪逼他吃藥讓下體硬硬，要他跟另一男子連續23小時啪啪啪。<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，南非約翰尼斯堡一名50歲男子受到了創傷，因為他被迫連續23小時啪啪啪，他指出從沒想過會被綁架，被帶到帕克通尼安普羅提(Braamfontein)的一間房子內。男子說被綁架時他被纏上眼罩，當貨車載他到目的地，「當她們拿下眼罩後，發現我被帶到一間臥室，裡面有一個講塞索托語(Sesotho)的女人，和一個穿著紅色短褲的印度男子」。<br />\n男子說，綁匪給他了一顆藥丸讓他下體保持硬硬，並且強迫他跟印度男子啪啪啪，女子則是在旁拍攝雙方的激戰過程，「她們第二天早上才讓我離開」。警方發言人姆貝利（Xoli Mbele）指出，該起綁架性侵案已經在調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190228/640_7ee36a44a7428970bdc32b80da93ba68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190228%2F640_7ee36a44a7428970bdc32b80da93ba68.jpg&h=c9abddec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c1c994f073a442119f31a63d946363e15de6d95","tid":1039924,"uid":197857,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"痴線 好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079118babed340a2bca3bd2c87fb983e6e73cef8","tid":1039924,"uid":150678,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"並且強迫他跟印度男子啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迫人屌屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1bf3ae2cbf4a17737cb347f30a650d88c2bc98","tid":1039924,"uid":26773,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T18:55:41.000Z"